public class ClaimContact
extends com.guidewire.pl.persistence.code.BeanBase
implements Retireable, Extractable, EventAware, ContactHandle
    ClaimContact Links a contact to a claim. This entity also contains an array to the roles played by the contact on the claim. Changes to the related Contact or the Roles array triggers validation.
